# Draftr Quick Test (5 Commands)

Quick test to verify Draftr access and browser automation works.

## Keywords
draftr, test, quick, verify

---

## Step 1: Navigate to Draftr
```mcp
{
  "tool": "browser_navigate",
  "params": {
    "url": "https://webpub.autodesk.com/draftr/"
  }
}
```

## Step 2: Wait for page
```mcp
{
  "tool": "browser_wait_for",
  "params": {
    "time": 5
  }
}
```

## Step 3: Take snapshot
```mcp
{
  "tool": "browser_snapshot",
  "params": {}
}
```

## Step 4: Take screenshot
```mcp
{
  "tool": "browser_take_screenshot",
  "params": {
    "filename": "draftr-loaded.png",
    "type": "png"
  }
}
```

## Step 5: Extract page title
```mcp
{
  "tool": "browser_evaluate",
  "params": {
    "function": "() => { return { title: document.title, url: window.location.href, ready: document.readyState }; }"
  }
}
```

## Expected Result
- Navigates to Draftr
- Waits 5 seconds
- Takes snapshot and screenshot
- Returns page title and URL
